rows.label: tlk70000055_04_msg0001
rows.name:
Noel seems really down
lately. What with everything
that's been going on.

rows.label: tlk70000055_04_msg0002
rows.name:
He's usually such a carefree
dolt, it worries me to see him
worrying for a change...

rows.label: tlk70000055_04_msg0003
rows.name:
Excuse me, I was out of
line calling him a dolt
just then. That was rude.

rows.label: tlk70000055_04_msg0004
rows.name:
Ugh! Why do I always do this?! I
open my big mouth and say something
I shouldn't. It's infuriating.

rows.label: tlk70000055_04_msg0005
rows.name:
Noel was the first friend I made in
the resistance. I'm just frustrated
that I can't do more to help him...
